column3:
もっとだ……

もっと トルネードの中心に……
上手く乗らないと……
column4:
Not enough.I must stay in the eye of the whirlwind...
must push myself harder...

column3:
覗き見なんて いい趣味じゃないよね？
姫……
column4:
You know, your highness...
it's rude to eavesdrop.

column3:
ごめんなさい……
村で ここにいると伺ったので
column4:
My apologies. I went to the village, and
I was told I could find you here.

column3:
……分かってるよ
この間の返事だろ？
column4: You have need of me. To defeat Calamity Ganon.

column3:
厄災ガノンの討伐……
受けてやってもいいよ
column4:
To slay the beast once and for all...
It will be my great pleasure.

column3:
ありがとう リーバル
私達には貴方の力が必要……
column4:
Thank you, Revali. If we work together,
I'm certain we'll be able to defeat—

column3: この僕が援護の大役を仰せつかる事になる……
column4: I know I play the biggest part in helping that, ahem...

column3:
たしか退魔の剣の騎士……
だっけ？
column4:
that little knight with the darkness-sealing sword.
Correct?

column3: 彼が今の技を見て自信を無くしても……
column4:
Well, if he loses his confidence after
seeing me in action...
